# Conversion of a mockup to a webpage.
This repo is for simple mockup to webpage conversion experimentation. Also this is an experimental github auto site generation. Want to see what I am working on? check out [@vgkrish](http://twitter.com/vgkrish) on twitter
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
